<L>__{interior dalai lama's private room night}
<A>__{the dalai lama sits at his desk, writing a letter. the radio is on. it is the bbc with news of a communist advantage in kuomintang china. norbu thundrup enters. the boy looks up.}
<C>__{tenzin gyatso}
<D>__{listen to this, norbu.}
<P>__{(he reads):}
<D>__{to mr truman the president of the united states of america i am glad that you are enjoying the best of health and doing good service to uplift the happiness and prosperity of the whole world. here, i am well and doing my best for the religion of lord buddha and welfare of all beings. this is all, so far.}
<C>__{norbu thundrup}
<D>__{reting rinpoche has died in prison.}
<A>__{tenzin gyatso lays down his pen.}
